        "description": "<p>Notice bar is simple but powerful plugin to create and display custom Notice bars in WordPress websites. It helps website admins to effectively convey notices, information &amp; messages to their visitors swiftly. With user friendly interface, tons of options to toggle and multiple notice types, Notice Bar is undoubtedly one of  best notice bar plugin for WordPress websites.<\/p>\n<h4>Some Useful Links<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plugin : <a href=\"http:\/\/wensolutions.com\/plugins\/notice-bar\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Homepage<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/wensolutions.com\/contact\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Support Forum<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<h4>Uploading in WordPress Dashboard<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to the &#8216;Add New&#8217; in the plugins dashboard<\/li>\n<li>Navigate to the &#8216;Upload&#8217; area<\/li>\n<li>Select <code>notice-bar.zip<\/code> from your computer<\/li>\n<li>Click &#8216;Install Now&#8217;<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin in the Plugin dashboard<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Using FTP<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Download <code>notice-bar.zip<\/code><\/li>\n<li>Extract the <code>notice-bar<\/code> directory to your computer<\/li>\n<li>Upload the <code>notice-bar<\/code> directory to the <code>\/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/code> directory<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin in the Plugin dashboard<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>3.1.2<\/h4>\n<p>Release Date: 15th January, 2024<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed select input width issue.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed date picker dackground issue.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.1.1<\/h4>\n<p>Release Date: 25th July, 2023<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed escaping issue.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed translation issue.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.1.0<\/h4>\n<p>Release Date: 7th July, 2023<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility tested with WordPress 6.2.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed slides notice issue\n<ul>\n<li>arrow issue <\/li>\n<li>content display issue <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0.0<\/h4>\n<p>Release Date: 22nd June, 2022<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility tested with WordPress 6.0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Enhancement:<br \/>\n* Added multiple positions for Notice bars.<br \/>\n* Added varieties of configurations for each sections like width, color etc.<br \/>\n* Added Enable\/Disable option for each sections.<br \/>\n* Added hide\/unhide option for each sections for mobile.<br \/>\n* Added total 8 types of Notice bars.<br \/>\n* Added multiple close actions with cookie timer.<br \/>\n* Added scheduling option for Notice bars.<br \/>\n* Added animations for the  plain text Notice.<br \/>\n* Added subscription form with subscribers list.<br \/>\n* Added option to hide\/unhide number of tweets and profile picture for  Twitter tweets.<br \/>\n* Sliding news ticker with multiple configurations.<br \/>\n* Added page display control for individual Notice bars.<br \/>\n* Added separate settings page with debug mode enable\/disable option.<br \/>\n* Shortcodes support.<\/p>\n<h4>2.1.0<\/h4>\n<p>Release Date: 1st February, 2022<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility tested with WordPress 5.9.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.9<\/h4>\n<p>Release Date: 28th December, 2021<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility tested with WordPress 5.8.2.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.8<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility testing with WordPress version 5.3.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.7<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Test compatibility.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Font size option and ticker bug has been removed.<\/li>\n<li>Did Small CSS fixing.<\/li>\n<li>Fixes : Minor settings issue.<\/li>\n<li>Tested Upto WordPress 5.2.2<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Font size option has been removed. <\/li>\n<li>POT file added.<\/li>\n<li>Compatibility testing with WordPress version 4.6.1.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added body class on notice-bar open and close conditions.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed functionality before v2.0.0. Backup your files and database before switching into latest version. <\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added tabs functionality<\/li>\n<li>Reduced width of the option field<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed Slider layout issue for version 2.0.1<\/li>\n<li>Fixed few css issue<\/li>\n<li>Added Debug Mode<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated with major change in UI <\/li>\n<li>Added new options such as news ticker, slider and social icons<\/li>\n<li>Added different styling options such as background color, font color, social icons color, social icons color hover, anchor links color, anchor links color on hover<\/li>\n<li>Added Settings section to switch between new and old version<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1358080\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1358080\" alt=\"Plugin Settings\"><\/a><p>Plugin Settings<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1358080\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1358080\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=1358080\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=1358080\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=1358080\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=1358080\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=1358080\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/notice-bar\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=1358080\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Doesnt show for non-logged in users<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/rustysyris\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/dce6eb96cf46820c538ee99c11b484e5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/dce6eb96cf46820c538ee99c11b484e5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/rustysyris\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Russell Benzing <small>(rustysyris)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 25, 2020<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Doesnt show unless users are logged in...worthless.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Created a nice bar but it covered the site title and banner<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/adventureridingnz\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ab649d3b4bd10b2eac454c9cfb884b22?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ab649d3b4bd10b2eac454c9cfb884b22?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/adventureridingnz\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">AdventureRidingNZ<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 15, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Notice Bar created a nice eye catching banner but for my site it covered the entire site title and logo and there didn't seem to be any way to change that.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works Well<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/alienative\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/cf9b5f7e99f0be483211b1caa3d580dd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/cf9b5f7e99f0be483211b1caa3d580dd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/alienative\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alienative<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 15, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Works Well for me, it does what I needed, a simple notice bar with some basic HTMLK.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Can&#039;t add link<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nathanwells\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ee66334d0a7b6dcad241f2127237830c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/ee66334d0a7b6dcad241f2127237830c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nathanwells\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\"> <small>(nathanwells)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">February 3, 2017<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Made it useless for me. But the message works, so 3 stars.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice, but pro version missing some basic functions for the price<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/zobabe\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9da059f33d30b5be444aaa335c1fa01c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9da059f33d30b5be444aaa335c1fa01c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/zobabe\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ZoBabe<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 31, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It's a nice simple way to get a notice up quick, but was disappointed to pay for the pro-version and find it to be missing a couple of functions I would have really basic.\n  It needs an HTML section. I should be able to make a quick two line notice, with a header in a larger font.\n  It needs a cookies option. If someone closes it, it really doesn't need to keep popping up every time they navigate to a new page.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">EXCELLENT PLUGIN... Fails on Safari<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/kelleychambers\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/aec834ba1e5713c972db88977482e187?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/aec834ba1e5713c972db88977482e187?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/kelleychambers\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kelleychambers<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 8, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">This is a fantastic plugin that works AWESOME on Chrome and Firefox but <strong>FAILS miserably<\/strong> in Safari... this needs to be fixed ASAP! There are a TON of users, namely iOS users, who use Safari... it's a major browser! Thus, this plugin is NOT cross platform compatible and needs to be. Once this is fixed, I will rate as \"5\" stars as it will have earned it.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice simple solution<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/entertheraptor\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9603cccc880a8aa5f2a4abccee610e79?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9603cccc880a8aa5f2a4abccee610e79?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/entertheraptor\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">entertheraptor<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>Very simple but very effective. Just a good honest plugin that does what it says and just works. The only feature I would add would be scheduling or at least an option to have it auto disable at a set date and time.\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple - and exactly what I need<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/mizagorn\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/206bcf06688d32e017146eec40c7a991?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/206bcf06688d32e017146eec40c7a991?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/mizagorn\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Mizagorn<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>This is a great little tool!  Nothing fancy - no horizontal scrolling, sidebar widgets or anything else like that.<\/p>\n<p>Perfect for just your basic site-wide, dismissable notice.  All elements have CSS classes that you can style, so it's a breeze to customize the look.<\/p>\n<p>If you have a fixed header area (like with the Divi theme), you will want to adjust the z-index of the announcement container so that it will sit on top of the header area.<\/p>\n<p>Nice work and kudos for a job well done. :)\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simple, but effective.<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/f4tal1st\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/132f67a669042da68f48175dc45b7b5c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/132f67a669042da68f48175dc45b7b5c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/f4tal1st\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">1 <small>(f4tal1st)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>Very easy to customize and use plugin. If developer put a preview option, in-build CSS support and add more buttons to click - it will be even better. Thanks!\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
